(4, 1, '2013-11-28 01:18:54', '2013-11-28 01:18:54', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSo excited to finally announce our arrival to the neighbourhood! Thanks to Elena for the wicked signage!\r\n\r\nBread by Us is *STILL* on track for an early December opening!\r\nRenovations are underway and coming along beautifully. The team is pumped and ready to go as soon as we get the go-ahead. \r\nKitchen and bar equipment is rolling in. Opening celebrations are being finalized.\r\nJess is ripping through her list of 200 tasks to accomplish, totally un-phased...for now.\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_72" align="alignnone" width="300"]<a href="http://breadbyus.com/wp-content/uploads/post-1-e1385601937131.jpg"><img src="http://breadbyus.com/wp-content/uploads/post-1-e1385601937131.jpg" alt="Exterior temporary signage for Bread By Us" width="300" height="400" class="size-full wp-image-72" /></a> Exterior temporary signage for Bread By Us[/caption]<a href="http://breadbyus.com/wp-content/uploads/post-1-2.jpg"><img src="http://breadbyus.com/wp-content/uploads/post-1-2-e1385602298276.jpg" alt="post-1-2" width="300" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-83" /></a>', 'Grand Opening (December 2013)', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'grand-opening-december-2013', '', '', '2013-12-03 23:11:14', '2013-12-03 23:11:14', '', 0, 'http://breadbyus.com/?p=4', 0, 'post', '', 0),
