(129, 1, '2013-12-04 03:24:25', '2013-12-04 03:24:25', '[one_half]\r\n<h4>GET A HOLD OF US</h4>\r\n<strong>JESSICA</strong>\r\n\r\nBaker &amp; Owner\r\n\r\nT 613-890-1423\r\n\r\nE jessica@breadbyus.com\r\n\r\n<strong>SARAH</strong>\r\n\r\nBarista\r\n\r\nE sarah@breadbyus.com\r\n\r\nWe will be located on\r\n\r\n<strong>1065 Wellington St. West</strong>\r\n<strong> 613-422-5300 </strong>\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<h5>WORKING WITH US</h5>\r\nFrom the birth of the idea of this bakery, it has been about building a creative, viable, inspiring, and prosperous working environment for all those who come through our walls as workers. Here''s how we see it.\r\n\r\nEvery position is of value to the company. We are dedicated to Living Wages for all.\r\n\r\nCreativity flows more freely when hierarchical barriers are broken down or diminished.\r\n\r\nOur long-term planning, decision-making, and vision is directed by the team, depending on the skill-set and desires of those involved. Communication is key.\r\n\r\nWorkplace satisfaction and genuine and sustainable success for the business can only be achieved when workers feel invested. This is why Bread By Us practices profit sharing.\r\n\r\n[/one_half_last]', 'CONTACT US', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-04 03:24:25', '2013-12-04 03:24:25', '', 44, 'http://breadbyus.com/?p=129', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
